Wake Up, Ak'Anon!<br>
<br>
Open your eyes! The Gnomes of Ak'Anon have become the slaves of a Unnatural Monstrosity and you do not even know it!<br>
<br>
Try to remember back to the the days of our Founding Fathers, when Gnomish Intelligence and Ingenuity were the marvel of the world and we ruled as Masters in OUR kingdom beneath the ground.  Remember and mourn, for what have we become? A society of SLAVE mechanics and tinkers supporting a FALSE RACE of clockwork usurpers! Open your eyes and minds! Ask yourself these questions!<br>
<br>
WHY is the entire monetary supply of Ak'Anon in the complete control of CLOCKWORK bankers?<br>
<br>
WHY is the ONLY truly Gnomish merchant in Ak'Anon a NEWSPAPER BOY? WHY is EVERY OTHER trade in Ak'ANon, from jeweler to smith, reserved for the MECHANICAL ELITE?<br>
<br>
WHY are the best and most important posts within the AK'ANon defense manned by TICK-TOCK Troopers, while the truly heroic LIVING Gnome defenders are consigned to HARDSHIP POSTS in the Steamfront Mountains?<br>
<br>
WHY are the living conditions of Gnomes within AK'Anon somewhat less glamorous than those of a Troll living in Neriak?<br>
<br>
WHY are the BEST and BRIGHTEST of our race consigned to live as PIRATES and OUTCASTS instead of being allowed to rule IN OUR OWN CITY?<br>
<br>
BECAUSE you have become the slaves of the CLOCKWORK king, and have given YOUR BIRTHRIGHT as masters of your destiny into the hands of him and his Manufactured Henchmen.<br>
<br>
RISE UP, Gnomes of Ak'ANon. Throw off the tinkered chains of the TICK-TOCK TYRANT. Give your support to The Dark Reflection and renounce any allegiance to the TICK-TOCK TYRANT and those that support him. FIGHT the CLOCKWORK MENACE, until once again we are OUR OWN MASTERS!<br>
<br>
